io.lettuce.core.support

Class RedisClientFactoryBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.beans.factory.config.AbstractFactoryBean<T>
      • io.lettuce.core.support.LettuceFactoryBeanSupport<RedisClient>
        • io.lettuce.core.support.RedisClientFactoryBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Aware, BeanClassLoaderAware, BeanFactoryAware, DisposableBean, FactoryBean<RedisClient>, InitializingBean

    public class RedisClientFactoryBean
extends LettuceFactoryBeanSupport<RedisClient>
    Factory Bean for RedisClient instances. Needs either a URI or a RedisURI as input and allows to reuse ClientResources. URI Formats: redis-sentinel://host[:port][,host2[:port2]][/databaseNumber]#sentinelMasterId redis://host[:port][/databaseNumber]
    Since:
    3.0
    Author:
    Mark Paluch
    See Also:
    RedisURI, ClientResourcesFactoryBean
